snippet.title: Warframe | Jade Shadows Official Gameplay Trailer - Now Available On All Platforms!
snippet.description:
***Spoiler Warning***

Jade Shadows contains significant spoilers for Warframe! To ensure that all Tenno enjoy the best possible experience, we ask that you allow others to complete the Quest at their own pace, and to please be kind. If you’d like to discuss the Quest after playing (and we certainly expect that you will), please use spoiler tags so everyone can experience it as intended. Thank you!

---

On June 18, Warframe’s newest Cinematic Quest will reveal the tragic history of one of the Origin System’s most enduringly mysterious figures. Assume control of the Stalker, hunt your prey with deadly tools of assassination, and unravel a hidden secret so explosive that the Origin System will never be the same…

The Jade Shadows update is chock-full of additions including the 57th Warframe, Jade, the new Ascension game mode, a new Clan Operation: Belly of the Beast, plus Yareli Pandea, numerous QoL improvements, fresh Augments, Arcanes, Decrees and so much more.

For more details please visit: https://www.warframe.com/news/jade-shadows

►► WHAT IS WARFRAME? 

Join 70M+ registered players in Warframe, a cooperative, free-to-play third-person looter shooter set in a constantly evolving sci-fi universe. For more info, visit https://warframe.com.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayWarframe/
